            <p class="max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-8 font-light text-gray-500 md:mb-12 sm:text-xl dark:text-gray-400">Get the latest updates on new features, community tournaments, and exclusive content delivered right to your inbox.</p>
            <form action="#">
