                <div class="max-w-screen-sm mx-auto text-sm text-gray-500 newsletter-form-footer dark:text-gray-300 text-center">We care about the protection of your data. <a href="/privacy-policy" class="font-medium text-purple-600 dark:text-purple-500 hover:underline">Read our Privacy Policy</a>.</div>
